1
00:00:34,520 --> 00:00:35,470
Xiao Wuyi!

2
00:00:38,560 --> 00:00:40,000
Xiao Wuyi!

3
00:00:49,110 --> 00:00:50,030
It's Young Master Yao!

4
00:00:50,030 --> 00:00:51,030
Young Master Yao?

5
00:00:52,920 --> 00:00:54,180
He's still breathing.

6
00:00:54,200 --> 00:00:55,460
Where is His Highness?

7
00:00:59,320 --> 00:01:00,880
You're going to the battlefield,

8
00:01:00,880 --> 00:01:02,540
so you deserve the best horse.

9
00:01:02,560 --> 00:01:03,760
It can bring you home.

10
00:01:10,510 --> 00:01:11,680
Xiao Wuyi!

11
00:01:11,710 --> 00:01:12,640
Your Highness!

12
00:01:12,640 --> 00:01:13,789
Your Highness!

13
00:01:25,590 --> 00:01:26,789
Xiao Wuyi!

14
00:01:39,229 --> 00:01:40,039
Xiao Wuyi!

15
00:01:48,710 --> 00:01:50,640
I'll accept your Black Iron Sword.

16
00:01:57,350 --> 00:01:57,920
Yaoyao,

17
00:01:58,710 --> 00:01:59,560
you said you've been learning

18
00:01:59,560 --> 00:02:01,290
to say goodbye your whole life.

19
00:02:01,510 --> 00:02:02,480
So have I.

20
00:02:03,640 --> 00:02:04,770
My parents are gone.

21
00:02:05,230 --> 00:02:06,360
My homeland is lost.

22
00:02:06,950 --> 00:02:07,840
A name and a mission were

23
00:02:07,840 --> 00:02:08,750
forced upon me.

24
00:02:09,710 --> 00:02:10,840
Living in the world,

25
00:02:10,910 --> 00:02:12,400
I got to understand its ways,

26
00:02:12,400 --> 00:02:13,660
yet failing the grace.

27
00:02:14,800 --> 00:02:17,000
What I gained in my life is what I sought.

28
00:02:17,310 --> 00:02:19,240
Yet it is somehow not what I sought.

29
00:02:19,750 --> 00:02:21,520
There is neither anyone to blame

30
00:02:21,520 --> 00:02:23,380
nor anywhere to direct my hatred.

31
00:02:25,030 --> 00:02:26,690
The way of heaven is ruthless.

32
00:02:27,079 --> 00:02:29,079
Blood drenched the Central Plains.

33
00:02:29,120 --> 00:02:31,380
Women and children were reduced to dust.

34
00:02:31,750 --> 00:02:33,550
Though I'm merely a human being,

35
00:02:33,710 --> 00:02:35,370
I'm willing to be the backbone

36
00:02:35,960 --> 00:02:37,630
to rebuild the nation anew.

37
00:02:41,000 --> 00:02:41,590
Yaoyao,

38
00:02:42,310 --> 00:02:43,710
since you've made your promise,

39
00:02:43,710 --> 00:02:46,440
no matter who tries
to take you away in the future,

40
00:02:47,800 --> 00:02:49,560
I will never let you go again.

41
00:02:52,170 --> 00:02:53,640
But 3 months is too short.

42
00:02:57,470 --> 00:02:58,560
How about 3 years?

43
00:02:59,840 --> 00:03:01,840
Can't you just say you'll try harder

44
00:03:01,870 --> 00:03:02,870
to stay alive?

45
00:03:06,800 --> 00:03:07,520
Okay.

46
00:03:12,750 --> 00:03:14,750
Xiao Wuyi!

47
00:03:23,520 --> 00:03:25,560
Xiao Wuyi!

48
00:05:39,900 --> 00:05:44,050
[Key to the Phoenix Heart]

49
00:05:44,110 --> 00:05:47,010
[Episode 28]

50
00:05:48,270 --> 00:05:50,670
[Three years later, First Year of Hong]

51
00:05:50,870 --> 00:05:51,730
Is that the end?

52
00:05:51,950 --> 00:05:52,800
What about Xiao Wuyi?

53
00:05:52,800 --> 00:05:53,860
Is he dead or alive?

54
00:05:54,190 --> 00:05:55,120
Did the Xiao family really harm

55
00:05:55,120 --> 00:05:56,630
the An and Lu families back then?

56
00:05:56,630 --> 00:05:58,630
Did we win the battle at Dingfeng Slope?

57
00:05:58,630 --> 00:06:00,270
We won, of course!

58
00:06:01,000 --> 00:06:01,630
If not,

59
00:06:01,720 --> 00:06:03,630
why would His Majesty re-establish
Chang County in the northwest?

60
00:06:03,630 --> 00:06:04,240
That's right.

61
00:06:04,240 --> 00:06:06,510
The Xiao family has even
drafted a confession letter.

62
00:06:06,510 --> 00:06:08,000
It couldn't be fake, could it?

63
00:06:08,000 --> 00:06:10,330
Exactly! In the battle at Dingfeng Slope,

64
00:06:10,390 --> 00:06:12,720
our Ye's 40,000 Beifu soldiers

65
00:06:12,920 --> 00:06:15,450
confronted
Northern Qin's 100,000 soldiers

66
00:06:15,950 --> 00:06:19,070
and completely routed Northern Qin.

67
00:06:19,560 --> 00:06:22,950
In this battle, they not only wiped out
the main force of the Northern Qin army

68
00:06:22,950 --> 00:06:25,510
but also allowed 100,000 Ye citizens

69
00:06:25,510 --> 00:06:27,390
to return home safely.

70
00:06:27,830 --> 00:06:29,230
With the Eagle King dead,

71
00:06:29,510 --> 00:06:33,070
the little emperor of Northern Qin was
wary of his meritorious officials,

72
00:06:33,070 --> 00:06:35,360
causing chaos at the imperial court.

73
00:06:36,000 --> 00:06:39,120
And our Ye's Beifu soldiers,
after Prince Qi's...

74
00:06:39,140 --> 00:06:39,700
No,

75
00:06:39,920 --> 00:06:43,430
after His Majesty's Beifu Reform,

76
00:06:43,750 --> 00:06:45,310
they've made an army
of elite soldiers and generals,

77
00:06:45,310 --> 00:06:46,920
with the soldiers
and the people of one mind.

78
00:06:46,920 --> 00:06:50,630
This is all thanks to His Majesty.

79
00:06:50,750 --> 00:06:52,210
All thanks to His Majesty?

80
00:06:53,310 --> 00:06:54,680
I remember the Beifu Reform

81
00:06:54,680 --> 00:06:56,740
was first proposed by Xiao Wuyi, right?

82
00:06:56,740 --> 00:06:58,120
In the battle at Dingfeng Slope,

83
00:06:58,120 --> 00:06:59,600
were it not for him who risked his life,

84
00:06:59,600 --> 00:07:01,310
how could we've held off
the Eagle King's main force?

85
00:07:01,310 --> 00:07:02,720
Were it not for His Majesty's support,

86
00:07:02,720 --> 00:07:03,720
could Xiao Wuyi have

87
00:07:03,720 --> 00:07:05,120
carried out this reform?

88
00:07:05,120 --> 00:07:05,950
-He's right.
-Indeed.

89
00:07:05,950 --> 00:07:06,920
If His Majesty hadn't led the troops

90
00:07:06,920 --> 00:07:07,790
and united the soldiers,

91
00:07:07,790 --> 00:07:08,830
Xiao Wuyi would've

92
00:07:08,830 --> 00:07:09,830
died for nothing.

93
00:07:11,680 --> 00:07:12,750
Stop talking nonsense!

94
00:07:12,750 --> 00:07:14,070
That's not right.

95
00:07:14,750 --> 00:07:17,510
Back then,
were it not for Young Lord Xiao's support,

96
00:07:17,510 --> 00:07:18,270
His Majesty

97
00:07:18,390 --> 00:07:20,360
wouldn't have secured
his position as Regent.

98
00:07:20,360 --> 00:07:21,600
It's all in the past.

99
00:07:22,070 --> 00:07:23,270
Nowadays, His Majesty

100
00:07:23,270 --> 00:07:25,070
works day and night diligently,

101
00:07:25,360 --> 00:07:26,950
promotes talents from poor backgrounds,

102
00:07:26,950 --> 00:07:28,430
and abolishes harsh laws.

103
00:07:28,680 --> 00:07:30,880
His Majesty has the aura of a wise ruler.

104
00:07:31,630 --> 00:07:32,310
Anyway,

105
00:07:32,600 --> 00:07:34,159
is Xiao Wuyi dead or not?

106
00:07:34,159 --> 00:07:35,310
To explain it,

107
00:07:35,800 --> 00:07:37,000
we have to talk about

108
00:07:37,000 --> 00:07:39,270
the firearms
used on the battlefield that day,

109
00:07:39,270 --> 00:07:40,600
the caltrop fireballs!

110
00:07:41,110 --> 00:07:43,840
Looks like it's time for me
to return to Jiankang.

111
00:07:55,159 --> 00:07:55,950
Lady Yu,

112
00:07:56,510 --> 00:07:57,510
your son

113
00:07:58,000 --> 00:08:00,120
didn't come to the clinic with you today?

114
00:08:00,120 --> 00:08:00,920
He set up

115
00:08:00,920 --> 00:08:02,240
a trap at school today,

116
00:08:02,430 --> 00:08:04,120
splashing slops all over his teacher.

117
00:08:04,120 --> 00:08:06,320
The teacher made him stay to copy texts.

118
00:08:07,040 --> 00:08:09,310
Teenage boys always like making trouble.

119
00:08:09,310 --> 00:08:10,070
Yeah,

120
00:08:10,240 --> 00:08:11,360
I'm wondering who he takes after,

121
00:08:11,360 --> 00:08:13,070
tinkering with mechanisms every day.

122
00:08:13,070 --> 00:08:14,630
His father, his teacher, and I

123
00:08:14,630 --> 00:08:15,630
are not like that.

124
00:08:16,800 --> 00:08:17,600
Really?

125
00:08:26,730 --> 00:08:28,630
[Zhengtong Bookstore]

126
00:08:44,150 --> 00:08:44,870
Lady He.

127
00:08:46,120 --> 00:08:47,250
Here in the academy,

128
00:08:47,360 --> 00:08:48,420
I'm only a teacher.

129
00:08:49,550 --> 00:08:50,610
Greetings, Ms. He.

130
00:08:51,600 --> 00:08:53,720
Today we are studying the Announcement
of Duke Shao from the Book of Documents.

131
00:08:53,720 --> 00:08:54,720
Have you looked through it?

132
00:08:54,720 --> 00:08:56,870
Yes, we have.

133
00:09:00,200 --> 00:09:02,240
I don't have a copy of the Announcement

134
00:09:02,240 --> 00:09:03,770
of Duke Shao due to poverty.

135
00:09:07,240 --> 00:09:09,390
This bookstore now belongs to me.

136
00:09:10,150 --> 00:09:12,150
It stores the He family's book collection.

137
00:09:12,150 --> 00:09:13,080
Starting today,

138
00:09:13,200 --> 00:09:15,320
you can borrow and copy books as you like.

139
00:09:15,320 --> 00:09:17,000
I will only charge for ink and paper.

140
00:09:17,000 --> 00:09:18,270
Thank you, Ms. He.

141
00:09:18,550 --> 00:09:19,670
Thank you, Ms. He.

142
00:09:20,080 --> 00:09:22,390
"I plant beans
beneath the southern hills."

143
00:09:22,390 --> 00:09:24,440
"The weeds flourish,
yet the bean sprouts are sparse."

144
00:09:24,440 --> 00:09:27,500
"The weeds flourish,
yet the bean sprouts are sparse."

145
00:09:35,000 --> 00:09:36,390
Couldn't I just have it expedited back

146
00:09:36,390 --> 00:09:37,190
on horseback?

147
00:09:37,390 --> 00:09:39,650
Why did I have to bring it back
to Jiankang in person?

148
00:09:39,650 --> 00:09:43,080
[Li Mao, Emperor of Ye]

149
00:09:40,870 --> 00:09:43,030
The mineral map is a national secret.

150
00:09:43,630 --> 00:09:45,630
How could it be entrusted to others?

151
00:09:49,000 --> 00:09:51,530
These two places are
where the iron mines are.

152
00:09:53,390 --> 00:09:54,360
More mining?

153
00:09:54,870 --> 00:09:56,080
Are we going to war again?

154
00:09:56,080 --> 00:09:58,410
The Northern Qin's young emperor is dead.

155
00:09:59,600 --> 00:10:01,600
Rumor has it he was poisoned to death.

156
00:10:01,600 --> 00:10:02,670
The Eagle King's death

157
00:10:02,670 --> 00:10:04,960
dealt a devastating blow
to the Northern Qin's foundation.

158
00:10:04,960 --> 00:10:06,390
Now their princes are having infighting

159
00:10:06,390 --> 00:10:07,550
and ruling on their own.

160
00:10:07,550 --> 00:10:09,200
They're also facing the invasion
of Rong and Qiang.

161
00:10:09,200 --> 00:10:09,840
It's the perfect time

162
00:10:09,840 --> 00:10:12,630
for us to reclaim the Capital
in one fell swoop.

163
00:10:14,550 --> 00:10:17,750
Do you know that Northern Qin
has put a bounty on your head,

164
00:10:17,870 --> 00:10:19,720
and it's gone up to 1,000 taels of gold
in the black market now?

165
00:10:19,720 --> 00:10:21,650
Because of the caltrop fireballs?

166
00:10:22,510 --> 00:10:23,970
Then let them come and try.

167
00:10:24,790 --> 00:10:26,870
I know your lightness skill is
exceptional now,

168
00:10:26,870 --> 00:10:28,910
and you don't need anyone
to protect you at all.

169
00:10:28,910 --> 00:10:29,790
You even sent Qing Long

170
00:10:29,790 --> 00:10:31,120
and Yan Yue back to Beifu

171
00:10:31,320 --> 00:10:32,850
to be regional commanders.

172
00:10:34,080 --> 00:10:34,880
It's just that

173
00:10:36,200 --> 00:10:38,200
you used to love a lively atmosphere.

174
00:10:38,200 --> 00:10:40,200
Now traveling the world on your own,

175
00:10:40,390 --> 00:10:41,650
don't you feel lonely?

176
00:10:43,910 --> 00:10:45,840
Someone is with me on the same path,

177
00:10:45,960 --> 00:10:47,490
so I have never felt lonely.

178
00:11:04,120 --> 00:11:05,270
I felt something was wrong with you
when we tested

179
00:11:05,270 --> 00:11:06,790
the caltrop fireballs yesterday.

180
00:11:06,790 --> 00:11:07,650
What happened?

181
00:11:07,670 --> 00:11:09,550
There are too many impurities
in the stone fat.

182
00:11:09,550 --> 00:11:11,080
Inhaling it into the lungs when it burns

183
00:11:11,080 --> 00:11:11,810
causes this.

184
00:11:12,440 --> 00:11:13,240
What's more,

185
00:11:14,200 --> 00:11:16,330
the land where the stone fat has burned

186
00:11:16,790 --> 00:11:18,590
will be left completely barren.

187
00:11:18,670 --> 00:11:20,030
I have destroyed the designs

188
00:11:20,030 --> 00:11:21,490
for the caltrop fireball.

189
00:11:21,910 --> 00:11:23,160
The burned land at Dingfeng Slope

190
00:11:23,160 --> 00:11:24,240
back then

191
00:11:24,270 --> 00:11:25,730
could no longer be farmed.

192
00:11:26,240 --> 00:11:27,700
One deterrence is enough.

193
00:11:28,030 --> 00:11:29,480
If you insist on using caltrop fireballs

194
00:11:29,480 --> 00:11:30,750
to fight your way back to the Capital,

195
00:11:30,750 --> 00:11:32,150
you will lose people's support.

196
00:11:32,150 --> 00:11:34,370
Even if you trap me here
in Jiankang Palace,

197
00:11:34,370 --> 00:11:35,630
I still won't help you.

198
00:11:35,840 --> 00:11:37,440
Nobody asked you about this.

199
00:11:38,030 --> 00:11:39,150
Aren't you curious

200
00:11:39,390 --> 00:11:40,630
about the Beifu Commander

201
00:11:40,630 --> 00:11:42,290
for the expedition this time?

202
00:11:44,000 --> 00:11:45,400
It's none of my business.

203
00:11:47,320 --> 00:11:48,550
I appointed Old General Ruan,

204
00:11:48,550 --> 00:11:49,960
from the Beifu Yafu Camp.

205
00:11:50,790 --> 00:11:52,390
Only then did I find out that,

206
00:11:52,440 --> 00:11:53,500
during the Reform,

207
00:11:53,600 --> 00:11:56,080
Xiao Wuyi had been
training the camps to coordinate

208
00:11:56,080 --> 00:11:57,910
to restore the supervisory system.

209
00:11:57,910 --> 00:11:59,390
I suppose that was also when

210
00:11:59,390 --> 00:12:00,440
he started preparing for what

211
00:12:00,440 --> 00:12:02,100
would happen after his death.

212
00:12:02,270 --> 00:12:03,960
He was afraid
that one day when he was gone,

213
00:12:03,960 --> 00:12:05,290
the sharp blade of Beifu

214
00:12:05,440 --> 00:12:07,240
would hurt Ye instead.

215
00:12:08,360 --> 00:12:09,390
So he was trying

216
00:12:09,870 --> 00:12:10,790
to create a Beifu Army

217
00:12:10,790 --> 00:12:12,120
that would still fight

218
00:12:12,600 --> 00:12:13,480
for the people of Ye

219
00:12:13,480 --> 00:12:15,200
even without Xiao Wuyi.

220
00:12:19,150 --> 00:12:21,270
The one I sent
to supervise Beifu this time

221
00:12:21,270 --> 00:12:23,800
is my most trusted
Imperial Guard Commander.

222
00:12:24,000 --> 00:12:25,930
He used to be a member of Beifu, too.

223
00:12:26,030 --> 00:12:27,790
He was injured on the battlefield,

224
00:12:27,790 --> 00:12:28,650
and I saved him.

225
00:12:28,960 --> 00:12:30,690
Then we became sworn brothers.

226
00:12:31,150 --> 00:12:31,790
I trust him

227
00:12:32,600 --> 00:12:34,460
even more than I trusted Wuyi back then.

228
00:12:34,460 --> 00:12:36,920
I was still willing
to deliver this map today

229
00:12:36,960 --> 00:12:39,090
because if Xiao Wuyi were still alive,

230
00:12:39,150 --> 00:12:41,480
he'd definitely want me to come in person.

231
00:12:42,510 --> 00:12:44,370
He always wanted to see Ye reclaim

232
00:12:44,470 --> 00:12:46,360
its lost territory, including the Capital,

233
00:12:46,360 --> 00:12:47,360
with his own eyes.

234
00:12:47,910 --> 00:12:50,040
As for what you plan to do with the Beifu

235
00:12:50,090 --> 00:12:52,030
and who you plan to use to replace him,

236
00:12:52,030 --> 00:12:53,090
I don't care at all.

237
00:12:54,170 --> 00:12:54,970
Your Majesty,

238
00:12:55,680 --> 00:12:56,940
you've forgotten him.

239
00:12:57,000 --> 00:12:58,360
The world has forgotten him.

240
00:12:58,360 --> 00:12:59,160
But I haven't,

241
00:13:01,320 --> 00:13:02,480
and I never will.

242
00:13:08,230 --> 00:13:09,630
Jiankang is way too cold.

243
00:13:11,240 --> 00:13:13,100
I will never come back here again.

244
00:13:20,910 --> 00:13:22,570
She's still so hot-tempered.

245
00:13:36,390 --> 00:13:38,450
Where on earth is the Guangyang Gate?

246
00:13:46,790 --> 00:13:48,200
Which way should I go?

247
00:13:48,750 --> 00:13:49,480
Who's there?

248
00:13:53,320 --> 00:13:54,080
Who are you?

249
00:13:55,480 --> 00:13:56,870
The Consort of the Heir of Prince Jing'an.

250
00:13:56,870 --> 00:13:58,470
His Majesty invited me over.

251
00:13:58,480 --> 00:13:59,810
Why don't you go ask him?

252
00:14:05,270 --> 00:14:06,200
I wouldn't dare.

253
00:14:06,390 --> 00:14:07,920
Greetings, Your Highness.

254
00:14:08,440 --> 00:14:10,300
How do I get to the Guangyang Gate?

255
00:14:32,080 --> 00:14:33,030
Acting mysterious.

256
00:14:33,030 --> 00:14:35,230
Dare you go fight on a real battlefield?

257
00:14:56,510 --> 00:14:57,970
Commander, what's wrong?

258
00:15:00,480 --> 00:15:01,440
I'm fine.

259
00:15:02,630 --> 00:15:03,630
It's an old wound.

260
00:15:20,360 --> 00:15:22,600
Have you forgotten
what the miraculous doctor said?

261
00:15:22,600 --> 00:15:25,460
Your body won't allow you
to practice martial arts.

262
00:15:29,600 --> 00:15:30,870
Greetings, Your Majesty.

263
00:15:30,870 --> 00:15:31,510
Rise now.

264
00:15:36,720 --> 00:15:37,600
Given your physical condition,

265
00:15:37,600 --> 00:15:38,750
if you want to live long,

266
00:15:38,750 --> 00:15:40,150
you must rest well. Yet you insisted

267
00:15:40,150 --> 00:15:41,520
on going to the Northern Border.

268
00:15:41,520 --> 00:15:42,520
I've agreed to it.

269
00:15:43,120 --> 00:15:45,630
But I only allow you
to be a military supervisor.

270
00:15:45,630 --> 00:15:47,480
If you insist on going to the battlefield,

271
00:15:47,480 --> 00:15:49,000
I will issue an imperial edict

272
00:15:49,000 --> 00:15:50,600
to get you back immediately.

273
00:15:51,240 --> 00:15:52,630
Yes, Your Majesty.

274
00:15:55,240 --> 00:15:58,900
The Consort of the Heir of Prince Jing'an
came to the palace today.

275
00:15:59,510 --> 00:16:02,240
I heard you ran into each other
on the palace path.

276
00:16:04,550 --> 00:16:07,390
If I want to bring her into my harem,

277
00:16:08,840 --> 00:16:09,840
what do you think?

278
00:16:10,720 --> 00:16:11,550
I think...

279
00:16:20,670 --> 00:16:21,510
Never mind.

280
00:16:21,870 --> 00:16:23,080
She has deep affection

281
00:16:23,080 --> 00:16:24,150
for her husband.

282
00:16:24,670 --> 00:16:25,790
I am the Emperor.

283
00:16:26,550 --> 00:16:28,750
I can find any kind of beauty
in the future.

284
00:16:28,750 --> 00:16:30,480
Why limit myself to one person?

285
00:16:31,910 --> 00:16:33,910
Your main purpose
in going to the Northern Border this time

286
00:16:33,910 --> 00:16:35,310
is to mine the mountains.

287
00:16:36,080 --> 00:16:37,480
If you have any problems,

288
00:16:37,630 --> 00:16:38,960
ask the Heir's Consort.

289
00:16:44,120 --> 00:16:46,080
Your Majesty, I remember you once said

290
00:16:46,080 --> 00:16:48,540
that she owns the map
and caltrop fireballs.

291
00:16:49,000 --> 00:16:51,360
Are you truly going to let her
leave Jiankang?

292
00:16:51,360 --> 00:16:52,870
Do you have any better ideas?

293
00:16:52,870 --> 00:16:54,270
Why not detain her first,

294
00:16:54,390 --> 00:16:56,080
claim it's Northern Qin's doing,

295
00:16:56,080 --> 00:16:58,010
and use it as a valid reason for war?

296
00:16:58,840 --> 00:17:00,000
If I really detain her,

297
00:17:00,000 --> 00:17:02,330
she will blow up my whole Jiankang Palace.

298
00:17:02,390 --> 00:17:03,920
Even if she won't blow it up,

299
00:17:05,109 --> 00:17:07,480
I'm afraid
when a certain someone recalls everything,

300
00:17:07,480 --> 00:17:09,940
he will tear down
this Jiankang Palace, too.

301
00:17:13,440 --> 00:17:15,240
Life and death are

302
00:17:15,240 --> 00:17:16,839
the natural order of things.

303
00:17:16,920 --> 00:17:19,119
He's hurt this badly yet still not dead.

304
00:17:19,349 --> 00:17:20,790
What is it in this world

305
00:17:20,790 --> 00:17:22,650
that he clings to so desperately?

306
00:17:24,160 --> 00:17:26,480
Please save my brother, miraculous doctor.

307
00:17:26,480 --> 00:17:27,609
I heard that you have

308
00:17:27,750 --> 00:17:29,950
the power to bring the dead back to life.

309
00:17:30,270 --> 00:17:32,930
Now, only you can save my brother!

310
00:17:32,960 --> 00:17:34,720
That's not bringing the dead back to life.

311
00:17:34,720 --> 00:17:36,510
That's just because they weren't
truly dead.

312
00:17:36,510 --> 00:17:36,790
Wait!

313
00:17:36,790 --> 00:17:37,250
Doctor!

314
00:17:38,510 --> 00:17:40,440
Wuyi is still breathing right now.

315
00:17:40,950 --> 00:17:43,210
You once promised to save my life 3 times.

316
00:17:43,920 --> 00:17:45,590
Please fulfill your last promise.

317
00:17:45,590 --> 00:17:46,990
If you want me to save him,

318
00:17:47,030 --> 00:17:49,310
he must first be pushed
to the brink of death.

319
00:17:49,310 --> 00:17:51,170
It will require cutting him open.

320
00:17:51,400 --> 00:17:54,110
And even if he survives,
he will lose his memory.

321
00:17:56,510 --> 00:17:58,040
Whether he survives or dies

322
00:17:58,680 --> 00:17:59,720
is up to fate.

323
00:18:01,400 --> 00:18:03,330
I believe God will take pity on him.

324
00:18:04,000 --> 00:18:04,730
Don't worry.

325
00:18:05,270 --> 00:18:06,550
Xie Jiayu will be fine.

326
00:18:07,200 --> 00:18:08,880
And she will never betray Ye.

327
00:18:09,720 --> 00:18:11,270
You are going to the Northern Border.

328
00:18:11,270 --> 00:18:13,400
You still need a weapon that suits you.

329
00:18:13,750 --> 00:18:16,480
Miraculous Craft in Jiankang
can create anything.

330
00:18:16,480 --> 00:18:17,610
You can give it a try.

331
00:18:20,960 --> 00:18:22,020
Yes, Your Majesty.

332
00:18:26,680 --> 00:18:27,740
Miraculous Craft?

333
00:19:15,070 --> 00:19:16,790
Why did I draw this sword?

334
00:19:20,830 --> 00:19:22,480
-Great!
-Bravo!

335
00:19:27,680 --> 00:19:29,520
-Brilliant!
-Bravo!

336
00:19:28,690 --> 00:19:29,310
[Miraculous Craft]

337
00:19:31,270 --> 00:19:32,400
Is the manager here?

338
00:19:33,590 --> 00:19:34,440
The manager is not here.

339
00:19:34,440 --> 00:19:36,440
You can tell me if you have any needs.

340
00:19:36,960 --> 00:19:38,960
I heard that your workshop
can forge any kind of weapon

341
00:19:38,960 --> 00:19:40,760
according to the requirements.

342
00:19:41,160 --> 00:19:42,240
"Supervised by the government office.

343
00:19:42,240 --> 00:19:43,840
Honest with all customers."

344
00:19:44,000 --> 00:19:46,400
This is very exquisite.
Please take a look.

345
00:19:46,480 --> 00:19:47,030
This is not bad.

346
00:19:47,030 --> 00:19:47,440
Right?

347
00:19:48,750 --> 00:19:49,400
Okay.

348
00:19:50,000 --> 00:19:51,110
Come to pick it up in 3 months.

349
00:19:51,110 --> 00:19:52,170
It takes that long?

350
00:19:52,680 --> 00:19:53,720
I'm leaving soon.

351
00:19:54,200 --> 00:19:55,550
Can I talk to your manager in person?

352
00:19:55,550 --> 00:19:57,070
The manager doesn't meet people.

353
00:19:57,070 --> 00:19:58,400
This is a fixed rule.

354
00:19:58,640 --> 00:20:00,110
It's the same for everyone.

355
00:20:00,110 --> 00:20:01,110
If you can't wait,

356
00:20:01,440 --> 00:20:02,700
you'd better not wait.

357
00:20:04,850 --> 00:20:05,840
[Black Iron Sword]

358
00:20:06,670 --> 00:20:07,800
Who is your manager?

359
00:20:08,030 --> 00:20:09,110
The manager of our shop is

360
00:20:09,110 --> 00:20:10,350
the Grand Master

361
00:20:10,350 --> 00:20:12,070
of Beifu Directorate of Military Equipment

362
00:20:12,070 --> 00:20:14,930
as well as the Consort
of the Heir of Prince Jing'an.

363
00:20:16,720 --> 00:20:19,050
The Consort of the Heir of Prince Jing'an?

364
00:20:21,400 --> 00:20:22,400
How much is the deposit?

365
00:20:22,400 --> 00:20:24,240
No deposit is needed. Our manager said

366
00:20:24,240 --> 00:20:24,790
she'll cover the cost

367
00:20:24,790 --> 00:20:27,000
of materials
if we fail to forge any items.

368
00:20:27,000 --> 00:20:28,400
What if I'm not in Jiankang

369
00:20:28,400 --> 00:20:29,550
when it's done?

370
00:20:29,830 --> 00:20:31,680
Don't worry. Our Miraculous Craft

371
00:20:31,680 --> 00:20:33,940
has branches in both Ye and Northern Qin.

372
00:20:34,030 --> 00:20:35,030
Take your receipt

373
00:20:35,070 --> 00:20:36,960
and claim it at the nearest branch.

374
00:20:36,960 --> 00:20:37,680
In a month,

375
00:20:37,750 --> 00:20:38,750
the Ye Xing caravan

376
00:20:38,750 --> 00:20:39,790
guarantees on-time delivery

377
00:20:39,790 --> 00:20:41,120
within Ye's territory.

378
00:20:41,310 --> 00:20:42,310
Cash on delivery.

379
00:20:43,310 --> 00:20:44,510
Here is your receipt.

380
00:21:16,030 --> 00:21:17,070
Prayer tree.

381
00:21:17,790 --> 00:21:18,750
Yin-Yang Tree

382
00:21:24,110 --> 00:21:24,790
Xiao Wuyi,

383
00:21:25,590 --> 00:21:28,070
could it be that you're actually not dead?

384
00:21:30,440 --> 00:21:31,700
Listen to my analysis.

385
00:21:32,310 --> 00:21:32,840
Firstly,

386
00:21:33,480 --> 00:21:35,160
I didn't even see your body.

387
00:21:36,510 --> 00:21:37,590
Maybe you felt that

388
00:21:38,640 --> 00:21:40,370
being Xiao Wuyi in this life was

389
00:21:40,640 --> 00:21:41,570
too exhausting,

390
00:21:42,110 --> 00:21:43,570
so you wanted to take a rest

391
00:21:44,160 --> 00:21:45,560
and found a place to hide.

392
00:21:46,640 --> 00:21:48,040
When you are well rested,

393
00:21:48,480 --> 00:21:49,810
you will come back to me.

394
00:21:52,640 --> 00:21:54,040
Doesn't that make sense?

395
00:21:56,240 --> 00:21:56,840
Secondly,

396
00:21:58,160 --> 00:21:59,070
you promised me

397
00:21:59,550 --> 00:22:00,680
you would come back.

398
00:22:01,400 --> 00:22:02,660
You have accomplished

399
00:22:05,070 --> 00:22:06,110
everything else.

400
00:22:07,880 --> 00:22:09,880
Xiao Wuyi is always a man of his word.

401
00:22:10,550 --> 00:22:11,610
You couldn't break

402
00:22:11,920 --> 00:22:13,320
your promise on this one,

403
00:22:14,030 --> 00:22:14,710
right?

404
00:22:16,160 --> 00:22:17,310
Why does she feel

405
00:22:18,440 --> 00:22:20,110
so familiar to me?

406
00:22:22,270 --> 00:22:25,330
Why am I feeling an inexplicable heartache
and crying?

407
00:23:07,590 --> 00:23:09,520
But even if you broke your promise,

408
00:23:10,270 --> 00:23:12,270
when we meet in heaven in the future,

409
00:23:13,200 --> 00:23:14,600
I will still forgive you.

410
00:23:15,830 --> 00:23:19,030
You had such a hard,

411
00:23:20,160 --> 00:23:20,890
tiring life.

412
00:23:22,790 --> 00:23:24,520
So I won't blame you for wanting

413
00:23:25,240 --> 00:23:26,070
to rest early.

414
00:23:32,200 --> 00:23:33,200
What do you think?

415
00:23:33,640 --> 00:23:34,640
Am I so generous?

416
00:23:36,350 --> 00:23:37,310
You were lucky

417
00:23:39,110 --> 00:23:40,370
to have me as your wife.

418
00:23:46,510 --> 00:23:47,240
Xiao Wuyi,

419
00:23:50,350 --> 00:23:51,310
I miss you.

420
00:23:54,510 --> 00:23:56,240
I promised you my eternal love.

421
00:23:57,680 --> 00:23:58,790
If you can hear me,

422
00:23:59,550 --> 00:24:00,810
just turn into the wind

423
00:24:00,830 --> 00:24:01,790
or the rain

424
00:24:03,160 --> 00:24:04,490
and meet me in my dreams.

425
00:24:09,960 --> 00:24:11,360
My wish came true so soon?

426
00:24:31,640 --> 00:24:33,480
The younger generation is getting worse.

427
00:24:33,480 --> 00:24:36,140
Go back and practice more
if you want to catch me.

428
00:24:48,830 --> 00:24:51,050
♪ Weave our devotion
into a melody of two hearts ♪

429
00:24:51,070 --> 00:24:53,370
♪ Mirror a gaze of stars and moon ♪

430
00:24:53,710 --> 00:24:56,980
♪ Forever illuminate each other's nights ♪

431
00:24:55,240 --> 00:24:55,970
Are you okay?

432
00:24:56,270 --> 00:24:57,000
Thank you.

433
00:24:58,840 --> 00:25:01,360
♪ The truest, most profound affection ♪

434
00:25:01,390 --> 00:25:03,390
♪ An eternal vow ♪

435
00:25:02,830 --> 00:25:03,830
If this is all he's got,

436
00:25:03,780 --> 00:25:08,190
♪ To be each other's forever ♪

437
00:25:04,160 --> 00:25:06,220
how dare he want to replace Xiao Wuyi?

438
00:25:08,790 --> 00:25:09,270
Hold on...

439
00:25:08,930 --> 00:25:13,230
♪ You enter my dreams,
permeating the crevices of my heart ♪

440
00:25:13,490 --> 00:25:15,490
♪ Every inch of longing ♪

441
00:25:15,520 --> 00:25:19,230
♪ Tugs at unspeakable fantasies ♪

442
00:25:19,260 --> 00:25:23,360
♪ Know that your heart is my heart ♪

443
00:25:23,740 --> 00:25:25,990
♪ Cherishing each other ♪

444
00:25:26,010 --> 00:25:30,600
♪ We will never be alone ♪

445
00:25:32,000 --> 00:25:33,750
♪ In the endless stream of time ♪

446
00:25:33,780 --> 00:25:36,610
♪ My life's every wish is for you ♪

447
00:25:36,640 --> 00:25:41,600
♪ All the sweet nothings in the world
fall short ♪

448
00:25:42,430 --> 00:25:44,110
♪ As time flows gently ♪

449
00:25:44,140 --> 00:25:46,750
♪ Hold each other and seal our vows ♪

450
00:25:46,780 --> 00:25:48,320
♪ Whatever the path ♪

451
00:25:48,340 --> 00:25:52,600
♪ I just want to be with you
for all time ♪

452
00:25:51,000 --> 00:25:53,350
-Xiao Wuyi and Xie Jiayu,
-Xiao Wuyi and Xie Jiayu,

453
00:25:52,890 --> 00:25:54,480
♪ A lifelong promise ♪

454
00:25:54,000 --> 00:25:55,550
-pledge the eternal love.
-pledge the eternal love.

455
00:25:54,500 --> 00:25:57,170
♪ My life's every moment is for you ♪

456
00:25:57,190 --> 00:25:59,190
♪ After all of it ♪

457
00:25:59,220 --> 00:26:02,030
♪ May all your dreams be realized ♪

458
00:26:03,070 --> 00:26:04,440
♪ Just you and me ♪

459
00:26:04,460 --> 00:26:07,640
♪ From dawn to dusk, year after year ♪

460
00:26:08,080 --> 00:26:13,850
♪ Hand in hand, let's experience
the bittersweet flavors of earthly life ♪

461
00:26:17,830 --> 00:26:18,640
Come take a look.

462
00:26:18,640 --> 00:26:19,940
Freshly steamed buns and stuffed buns.

463
00:26:19,940 --> 00:26:20,670
Look.

464
00:26:23,040 --> 00:26:24,510
They're freshly made and hot.

465
00:26:24,510 --> 00:26:25,570
Really delicious.

466
00:26:38,070 --> 00:26:39,130
Nanxing! Nanxing!

467
00:26:39,590 --> 00:26:41,650
I think I just saw the Heir's Consort.

468
00:26:43,200 --> 00:26:44,480
There's no way.

469
00:26:44,790 --> 00:26:45,680
Her Ladyship was in Cangwu County

470
00:26:45,680 --> 00:26:47,160
when she wrote me last time.

471
00:26:47,160 --> 00:26:47,680
But...

472
00:26:47,920 --> 00:26:48,850
As you also know,

473
00:26:49,160 --> 00:26:49,960
both Jiankang

474
00:26:50,070 --> 00:26:51,240
and the Northern Border

475
00:26:51,240 --> 00:26:53,640
are places of heartbreak for Her Ladyship.

476
00:26:54,790 --> 00:26:55,550
Now, Her Ladyship

477
00:26:55,550 --> 00:26:57,280
prefers to stay in warm places.

478
00:26:57,510 --> 00:26:58,370
But just now...

479
00:27:00,550 --> 00:27:01,160
Mr. Jing.

480
00:27:02,510 --> 00:27:04,070
Did you record the accounts wrong again?

481
00:27:04,070 --> 00:27:04,920
No way.

482
00:27:05,440 --> 00:27:07,550
The inventory and the numbers don't match.

483
00:27:07,550 --> 00:27:08,110
Come with me.

484
00:27:08,110 --> 00:27:09,710
I'll go take a look. Let's go.

485
00:27:31,880 --> 00:27:33,770
[Black Iron Sword]

486
00:27:46,720 --> 00:27:47,680
This is

487
00:27:48,640 --> 00:27:49,840
the Black Iron Sword.

488
00:27:53,920 --> 00:27:54,510
My Lady!

489
00:27:55,640 --> 00:27:58,440
This is the Black Iron Sword
I forged for Xiao Wuyi.

490
00:27:58,640 --> 00:28:00,160
Where is the person who wanted this sword?

491
00:28:00,160 --> 00:28:01,140
When did he or she come?

492
00:28:01,140 --> 00:28:02,400
H-He came this morning.

493
00:28:02,400 --> 00:28:03,380
What did he look like?

494
00:28:03,380 --> 00:28:04,680
What kind of clothes was he in?

495
00:28:04,680 --> 00:28:05,440
He wore

496
00:28:06,080 --> 00:28:08,480
an Imperial Guard uniform
and a scary mask.

497
00:28:09,680 --> 00:28:11,550
The one I sent
to supervise Beifu this time

498
00:28:11,550 --> 00:28:13,480
is my most trusted
Imperial Guard Commander.

499
00:28:13,480 --> 00:28:15,350
He used to be a member of Beifu, too.

500
00:28:15,350 --> 00:28:17,110
He was injured on the battlefield,

501
00:28:17,110 --> 00:28:17,970
and I saved him.

502
00:28:18,320 --> 00:28:20,050
Then we became sworn brothers.

503
00:28:47,920 --> 00:28:50,060
[Xuanzheng Hall]

504
00:28:54,720 --> 00:28:56,510
Xiao Wuyi is not dead, right?

505
00:28:57,200 --> 00:28:57,960
Where is he?

506
00:28:58,070 --> 00:28:59,400
What on earth happened?

507
00:29:01,270 --> 00:29:02,070
You may leave.

508
00:29:02,350 --> 00:29:03,080
Understood.

509
00:29:11,310 --> 00:29:12,000
Xiao Wuyi,

510
00:29:12,440 --> 00:29:14,300
let me be your strongest support.

511
00:29:14,590 --> 00:29:15,270
You and I

512
00:29:15,830 --> 00:29:17,160
will walk the same path.

513
00:29:27,020 --> 00:29:27,710
Xiao Wuyi,

514
00:29:27,150 --> 00:29:30,570
♪ A dying memory glimmers low ♪

515
00:29:28,240 --> 00:29:30,070
I don't just want
to walk the same path as you.

516
00:29:30,070 --> 00:29:30,920
I want to be

517
00:29:31,230 --> 00:29:34,900
♪ You appear, but I can't hold you so ♪

518
00:29:31,440 --> 00:29:32,970
together with you forever.

519
00:29:35,010 --> 00:29:39,380
♪ Time itself comes to a sudden halt ♪

520
00:29:39,740 --> 00:29:42,430
♪ So desolate ♪

521
00:29:43,010 --> 00:29:46,680
♪ I traded obsession for this loss ♪

522
00:29:46,700 --> 00:29:50,240
♪ If I could lay my heart bare and cross ♪

523
00:29:50,430 --> 00:29:55,770
♪ Would you once more have pity on me ♪

524
00:29:50,510 --> 00:29:51,640
Do you admit defeat?

525
00:29:56,410 --> 00:29:59,850
♪ If the heavens should change
and fate tear me apart ♪

526
00:29:59,870 --> 00:30:03,870
♪ Yet still cannot undo one beat
of my heart's art ♪

527
00:30:04,000 --> 00:30:07,720
♪ I've traveled so far—
the day I find you again ♪

528
00:30:04,480 --> 00:30:04,880
Jiayu!

529
00:30:07,740 --> 00:30:11,440
♪ I fear you might have forgotten me ♪

530
00:30:08,240 --> 00:30:09,500
Xiao Wuyi, let go of me!

531
00:30:11,690 --> 00:30:14,510
♪ I fear no doom of endless karmic pain ♪

532
00:30:12,530 --> 00:30:13,260
Grand Tutor.

533
00:30:14,540 --> 00:30:17,030
♪ Only that you drift far from my side ♪

534
00:30:17,290 --> 00:30:21,460
♪ Apart from you,
the world is an endless night ♪

535
00:30:21,480 --> 00:30:25,080
♪ Even if my beating heart
wears thin and fades ♪

536
00:30:25,330 --> 00:30:27,100
♪ I'd choose this fate
till death's final line ♪

537
00:30:27,330 --> 00:30:29,950
♪ I only hope the mortal lands ♪

538
00:30:29,970 --> 00:30:32,640
♪ Can grant our wishes ♪

539
00:30:31,310 --> 00:30:31,960
Xiao Wuyi!

540
00:30:32,510 --> 00:30:33,880
Give Yaoyao back to me.

541
00:30:32,900 --> 00:30:37,140
♪ Through endless night,
let heaven and earth fall apart ♪

542
00:30:33,960 --> 00:30:34,640
Xiao Wuyi!

543
00:30:37,470 --> 00:30:41,640
♪ I'd bid farewell to every worldly part ♪

544
00:30:37,550 --> 00:30:38,240
Xiao Wuyi,

545
00:30:39,110 --> 00:30:40,790
husband and wife share the same fate.

546
00:30:40,790 --> 00:30:42,070
I only want you to live.

547
00:30:41,950 --> 00:30:46,790
♪ Just to gaze upon you one last time ♪

548
00:30:43,200 --> 00:30:44,400
Having you by my side,

549
00:30:45,680 --> 00:30:47,880
I, Xiao Wuyi, have no regrets in my life.

550
00:31:00,430 --> 00:31:03,850
